condition.narrative: Establish and thereafter maintain the Project Steering Committees at Federal, and State levels to provide overall guidance andoversight for the Project at the Federal, State, and Local Government Area levels, Schedule 2 Section 1.

The Recipient shall ensure that each Participating State makes Livelihood Grants to Beneficiaries in accordance with eligibilitycriteria and procedures acceptable to the Association and elaborated in the PIM, Section I of Schedule 2 to the Financing Agreement(FA).
The Recipient shall ensure that the Project is carried out in accordance with the provisions of the ESMF, the RPF; and IntegratedPest Management Plan, Section I of Schedule 2 to the FA.
